snippet.title: Autopsy Simulator - Official Console Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't miss the Console Launch Trailer for Autopsy Simulator, an adventure simulation game developed by Woodland Games. Players will assume the role of an autopsy specialist to study realistic case files and guide their examinations. Utilizing medically authentic tools and procedures, players will learn all they can about the deceased before solving the mystery of their case. Autopsy Simulator is available now for PlayStation 5 (PS5) and Xbox Series X|S alongside PC.

#AutopsySimulator #Gaming #Games
